name: Advertising experiment #6
description: This is an advertising experiment. Owners of this OBJKT will be listed as "featured user" on the exploration tool <https://projects.stroep.nl/hicetnunc/> until 31/05/2021. On each page view the featured user is randomly chosen. The data will be fetched using the API from <https://better-call.dev>, so once collected the collector should be featured directly.
